  29:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     The Timer Extended features include:
  30:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (#) Complementary outputs with programmable dead-time for :
  31:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         (++) Output Compare
  32:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         (++) PWM generation (Edge and Center-aligned Mode)
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccMbhVRt.s 			page 2


  33:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         (++) One-pulse mode output
  34:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (#) Synchronization circuit to control the timer with external signals and to
  35:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         interconnect several timers together.
  36:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (#) Break input to put the timer output signals in reset state or in a known state.
  37:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****     (#) Supports incremental (quadrature) encoder and hall-sensor circuitry for
  38:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         positioning purposes
