1770:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c **** /**
1771:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @brief  Configure the TIM commutation event sequence.
1772:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @note  This function is mandatory to use the commutation event in order to
1773:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        update the configuration at each commutation detection on the TRGI input of the Timer,
1774:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        the typical use of this feature is with the use of another Timer(interface Timer)
1775:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        configured in Hall sensor interface, this interface Timer will generate the
1776:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        commutation at its TRGO output (connected to Timer used in this function) each time
1777:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *        the TI1 of the Interface Timer detect a commutation at its input TI1.
1778:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @param  htim TIM handle
1779:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @param  InputTrigger the Internal trigger corresponding to the Timer Interfacing with the Hall 
1780:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
1781:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR0: Internal trigger 0 selected
1782:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR1: Internal trigger 1 selected
1783:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR2: Internal trigger 2 selected
1784:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_ITR3: Internal trigger 3 selected
1785:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *            @arg TIM_TS_NONE: No trigger is needed
1786:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   * @param  CommutationSource the Commutation Event source
1787:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
